{"about_the_game":"The sun has stopped rising after a mysterious explosion at the top of an ancient tower.  You must gather your wits and survive eternal night in a world driven mad by apocalypse.  Every moment counts and every decision comes with consequences in the unforgiving forests of the Vlenfir Valley.  Grow, learn, adapt and equip your treasures; but be careful, something worse than death is coming for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Turn-based Tactics </h2><br>Plan your moves and lead your heroes to victory with superior tactics.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/page_description_combat_2.png?t=1667490733\" /><br><br>Engage your foe with a tactics system focused on deep melee interactions like flanking, opportunity attacks, engagement, and competence.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/page_description_tactics_opportunity_1.png?t=1667490733\" /><br><br>Use morale to terrify foes and bolster allies when their conviction wanes.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/page_description_combat_morale.png?t=1667490733\" /><br><br>Survive encounters with deadly bosses intent on ending your journey.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/page_description_bosses.png?t=1667490733\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Roguelike Progression</h2><br>No one lives forever so make every choice count.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/page_description_permadeath.png?t=1667490733\" /><br><br>Permanently unlock classes, recipes, and more through encounters and treasure rewards.  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/page_description_crafting.png?t=1667490733\" /><br><br>Every playthrough features new heroes, along with new enemies to defeat, encounters to discover, and treasure to find<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/page_description_world_2.png?t=1667490733\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Role-Playing </h2><br>Earn experience and customize your hero's skills and talents.  Add to their repertoir by discovering skill books and manuals throughout the world. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/page_description_skills.png?t=1667490733\" /><br><br>Use what you find or keep it to craft or sell.  Every item has value.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/page_description_gear_and_items.png?t=1667490733\" /><br><br>The choices you make can change the outcome of every encounter, along with randomized results to make every playthrough different.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/roguelike_storytelling.png?t=1667490733\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1667490733","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/page.bg.jpg?t=1667490733","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1667490733","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1667490733","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,2,5],"notes":"This game contains frequent gore and depictions of violence in varied scenes, especially during combat sequences.